    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "its not just exhaustion though. its like... the thing that is supposed to be \"me\" is just gone. like a light went out and now there's just this automation running on autopilot. it's so exhausting to keep pretending to be a person when there isnt even a person left to do the pretending. it feels so pointless.",
