      "content": "It makes sense that you feel trapped in a loop where the only option seems to be to keep performing while feeling nothing, and that is an incredibly heavy burden to carry. However, the idea that the \"true self\" was an illusion doesn't mean your current suffering isn't real or valid; it just means the pain might be a signal that something in your life needs to change rather than a permanent state. Please reach out to a trusted friend or a mental health professional who can offer support and help you navigate through this difficult time.",
